#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:4
msgid "Progress"
msgstr "Progress"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.desktop.in.in:5
msgid "Kanban style todo app"
msgstr "Aplicación de tareas pendientes estilo Kanban"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.desktop.in.in:7
msgid "Kanban;Todo;Progress;"
msgstr "Kanban;Tareas pendientes;Progress;"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:5
msgid "Kanban board application"
msgstr "Aplicación de tablero Kanban"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:29
#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:44
msgid "Dedicate a board for each of your projects"
msgstr "Dedica un tablero a cada uno de tus proyectos"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:34
#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:49
msgid "Organize your tasks in your own way"
msgstr "Organiza tus tareas a tu manera"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:39
#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:54
msgid "Fill your cards with adequate information"
msgstr "Rellena tus tarjetas con la información necesaria"

#: data/io.github.smolblackcat.Progress.metainfo.xml.in.in:59
msgid ""
"Whether you’re a software developer, a project manager, or simply someone "
"who enjoys keeping track of personal goals, Progress gives you the essential "
"framework to organize tasks effectively while also being simple and easy to "
"use."
msgstr ""
"Tanto si eres desarrollador de software, gestor de proyectos o simplemente "
"alguien a quien le gusta llevar un seguimiento de sus objetivos personales, "
"Progress te ofrece el marco esencial para organizar tus tareas de forma "
"eficaz, sin dejar de ser una herramienta sencilla y fácil de usar."

